Comment: 0,0:09:31.49,0:09:33.76,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,Hibiya
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.44,0:00:05.23,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,When watching TV,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.23,0:00:06.77,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,make sure the room is well lit,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.77,0:00:09.02,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,and watch from a distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.02,0:00:10.02,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.38,0:00:17.85,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-She's dead! {ep 29}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.85,0:00:21.93,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,But I have already narrowed down who the culprit is. {ep 29}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.92,0:00:25.88,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,That is one of those dying messages.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.88,0:00:27.04,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,I bet not.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.37,0:00:30.88,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.53,0:00:37.42,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,You were behind all of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.50,0:00:50.56,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,One who masters being a butler becomes the master of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.56,0:00:56.07,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The Butler War that shakes the planet has started!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.17,0:00:58.07,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,This week's Hayate is filled with suspense.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.25,0:01:01.07,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But please enjoy it with your entire family like you normally do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.85,0:02:43.44,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,The autumn wind really feels good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.44,0:02:45.54,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Yes it does, Milady.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.54,0:02:47.51,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,The foliage looks beautiful, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.14,0:02:50.85,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,It was good to come all the way to a hot spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.85,0:02:51.88,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.91,0:02:56.55,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,By the way Milady, which one is the inn we'll be staying at?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.55,0:02:57.57,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,That one!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.71,0:02:59.82,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,That?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.10,0:03:02.32,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, it's so classical.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.32,0:03:06.08,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,The best way to enjoy a hot spring is to waste time at a rotting inn.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.08,0:03:09.06,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,But I get this portentous feeling from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.06,0:03:09.61,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.61,0:03:11.77,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,It's emitting an untouchable vibe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.00,0:03:17.42,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,You just heard a scream from the inn, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.42,0:03:18.06,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.12,0:03:24.03,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.71,0:03:27.12,Default,Mak,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.60,0:03:34.59,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Um, you look different from the opening.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.79,0:03:38.06,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! That situation would make me unable to get married!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.87,0:03:41.14,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,I can smell a crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.14,0:03:42.67,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,You just committed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.13,0:03:47.30,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't expect to get caught up\Nin a murder case at a hot spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.30,0:03:48.82,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,How entertaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.82,0:03:50.88,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, we're in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.11,0:03:53.75,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,We must contact the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.75,0:03:55.09,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.09,0:03:56.98,Default,Ris,0000,0000,0000,,We have a problem. We have a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.98,0:03:58.35,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,There is no need for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.56,0:04:01.50,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Will always come to the absolute truth. {ep 29}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.50,0:04:03.55,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Appears to be a tsundere and has the brain of a NEET. {ep 29}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.84,0:04:06.16,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Her name is Detective Nagi! {ep 29}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.06,0:04:10.13,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,That bag for grade schoolers fits you surprisingly well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.32,0:04:13.36,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what you're supposed to jab at!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.65,0:04:15.81,Default,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.07,0:04:21.74,Default,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,I always thought of you as a hopeless sister, but who knew this would happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.24,0:04:24.78,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for you, but please hold yourself together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.78,0:04:26.56,Default,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.56,0:04:29.13,Default,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I have something I want you all to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.13,0:04:29.58,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.74,0:04:33.48,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,A video tape?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.48,0:04:37.87,Default,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. This just arrived for me by motorbike delivery.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.87,0:04:39.58,Default,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's something my sister took.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.41,0:04:46.26,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if it's recording okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.75,0:04:48.44,Default,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,This is this room, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.44,0:04:49.70,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.15,0:04:57.35,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Hina. By the time you watch this,\NI might already have become a star in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.67,0:05:01.05,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,I guess the saying that pretty people die young was true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.57,0:05:03.24,Default,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievable what she can say.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.24,0:05:05.45,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Um, the background has...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.71,0:05:11.83,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,To tell you the truth, I've been told to come\Nto this inn by an unknown individual through a letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.27,0:05:15.46,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like the person holds a grudge against me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.06,0:05:19.16,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,But I still don't have a clue who it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.16,0:05:22.73,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,I think the person should be coming to this room soon, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.09,0:05:25.40,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starting to lose interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.97,0:05:32.62,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Hina! If I die, then the person who killed me\Nwill be the next person who appears on this screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.62,0:05:36.39,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you catch that person and get all the reparations you can for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.39,0:05:37.31,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Do you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.45,0:05:39.40,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,She's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.41,0:05:42.81,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,It ends there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.81,0:05:44.92,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,No way, it stopped at the most crucial point.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.21,0:05:46.38,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,This is horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.38,0:05:50.61,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,It's as bad as a mother who tricks her children by calling a honey-coated cucumber a melon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.61,0:05:53.28,Default,Ris,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's as bad as saying pudding with soy sauce is sea urchin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.28,0:05:53.90,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.10,0:05:57.23,Default-alt,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}It's as bad as calling an orange with seaweed and soy sauce a salmon roe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.71,0:06:02.33,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,This tape... The criminal must have physically cut him or herself out of the tape, then sent it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.27,0:06:07.78,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,So, this is a challenge letter to me from the criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.21,0:06:12.78,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,But I have already narrowed down who the culprit is. {ep 29}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.16,0:06:15.57,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.57,0:06:17.33,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. The criminal is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.33,0:06:18.41,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,The criminal is?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.41,0:06:20.30,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,You!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.30,0:06:21.62,Default,Mak,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.62,0:06:24.73,Default,Mak,0000,0000,0000,,I'm only a guest staying next door.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.73,0:06:29.51,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,As well as a super side character\Nthat hasn't shown up since episode 23.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.51,0:06:32.54,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell everything that happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.51,0:06:31.34,Default-alt,Mak,0000,0000,0000,,I was in episode 25, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.09,0:06:36.71,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,You called the victim out and...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.21,0:06:39.42,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come any closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.42,0:06:41.05,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,You try and touch me,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.05,0:06:45.28,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,and I'll have you pay all my pub bills that have piled up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.27,0:06:53.22,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Using a polka-dot snake that just happened to pass by...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.53,0:06:59.93,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,That's what happened. So, isn't it a perfect deduction?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.93,0:07:01.66,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.66,0:07:05.64,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,You just copied the most famous trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.64,0:07:07.34,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Apologize to Mr. Doyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.86,0:07:09.71,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,You are under arrest.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.71,0:07:12.18,Default,Mak,0000,0000,0000,,No, it wasn't me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.18,0:07:13.96,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,I will hear no words from you. Give it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.96,0:07:14.88,Default,Mak,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.88,0:07:15.58,Default,Robo,0000,0000,0000,,Grab.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.86,0:07:17.35,Default,Robo,0000,0000,0000,,Break.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.77,0:07:20.84,Default,Robo,0000,0000,0000,,Don't treat my honey as a criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.84,0:07:22.05,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out, Milady.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.96,0:07:32.34,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Nice one, Hayate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.34,0:07:35.52,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Milady, the criminal seems to be someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.52,0:07:38.92,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, to be honest, I had that feeling, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.92,0:07:39.92,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.66,0:07:43.37,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Then the next most suspicious ones are you three.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.94,0:07:49.51,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.51,0:07:54.35,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,You called the victim out,\Nand using a polka-dot octopus that passed by...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.67,0:07:58.73,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,There you have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.73,0:08:00.77,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,What is this polka-dot octopus?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.77,0:08:02.64,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,We weren't even in that scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.64,0:08:04.89,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Stop resisting and be arrested!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.89,0:08:07.60,Default,Ris,0000,0000,0000,,There is someone else who's likely to have a motive, isn't there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.82,0:08:09.43,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Right, a motive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.87,0:08:12.06,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you have a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.06,0:08:15.67,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,An individual who probably holds\Nthe biggest grudge against the victim is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.67,0:08:18.47,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Who else other than the debt-ridden butler?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.89,0:08:22.53,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.53,0:08:25.65,Default-alt,All,0000,0000,0000,,Glare~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.87,0:08:25.65,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,All of you, please don't glare at me with those suspecting eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.12,0:08:28.63,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one person I trusted.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.63,0:08:30.19,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I said it's not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.62,0:08:33.42,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I told you it's not me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.24,0:08:36.46,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Using a polka-dot elephant that passed by...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.75,0:08:42.55,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,You look as if you wouldn't even kill an insect, and yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.06,0:08:44.31,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, is this Yama-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.35,0:08:49.89,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,I have the criminal in hand,\Nbut the victim won't be coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.03,0:08:53.12,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,How about we go to the roof top\Nfor another chat under the sunset?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.55,0:08:46.05,Default-alt,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Milady, your deductions are only taking place in the wilderness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.05,0:08:50.33,Default-alt,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Besides, the setting has changed from the inn to Africa all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.33,0:08:52.73,Default-alt,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}And who are you talking to, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.60,0:08:55.34,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.34,0:08:57.70,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,How many times do you have to kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.70,0:09:00.05,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,The story isn't progressing at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.05,0:09:03.10,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Mind you, it's really embarrassing to play dead in this outfit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.10,0:09:03.96,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Hinagiku!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.96,0:09:04.42,Default,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.65,0:09:06.69,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,You better do it properly as the script says.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.69,0:09:07.49,Default,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.90,0:09:08.86,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Collapse.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.10,0:09:14.50,Default,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.23,0:09:18.90,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,That has to be one of those dying messages.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.90,0:09:21.36,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,What's a dying message?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.36,0:09:23.24,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,You don't even know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.24,0:09:24.84,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.52,0:09:31.48,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,A dying message is a hint the victim leaves behind on purpose to aid later deduction.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.95,0:09:33.75,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.26,0:09:35.99,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,But, what's "Hibiya"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.99,0:09:37.59,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to explain again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.59,0:09:42.57,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Hibiya is an area in Tokyo made up of\Nthe Choyoda ward and Yuuraku-chou, close to Ginza.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.57,0:09:47.83,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,As a bit of trivia, this is where\Nthe very first street light in Japan was installed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.99,0:09:49.78,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need to know that kind of trivia.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.78,0:09:53.57,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, if we can decode this dying message, we can figure out who the criminal is, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.11,0:09:56.83,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,It's starting to become like a real detective story.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.83,0:09:57.72,Default,Ris,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.72,0:09:59.84,Default,Mak,0000,0000,0000,,But this is very hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.84,0:10:00.90,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.58,0:10:03.95,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,No, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.79,0:10:08.62,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,This is nowhere close to the mystery behind the pyramids and UFOs!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.03,0:10:10.46,Default,3,0000,0000,0000,,What did she say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.03,0:10:14.05,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I'm not sure about using that other glasses character.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.05,0:10:15.21,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.75,0:10:20.56,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,You, indeed, are my assistant. You have good instincts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.56,0:10:21.93,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,D-Do I?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.93,0:10:26.20,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,As he suggests, this crime was committed by a character that's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.08,0:10:28.27,Default,Robo,0000,0000,0000,,Another character?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.27,0:10:33.99,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. The criminal must be hiding somewhere after committing the murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.99,0:10:35.21,Default,Mak,0000,0000,0000,,And the location is?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.74,0:10:38.26,Default,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going to say Hibiya, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.13,0:10:41.15,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Take a good second look at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.34,0:10:45.59,Default,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,It says Hibiya no matter how you read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.59,0:10:50.69,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,No, the ********* seeds around it are part of the message, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.12,0:10:53.86,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Look, the written part is the right side of kanji.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.86,0:10:55.95,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,And if you treat the ********* seeds as radicals,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.48,0:11:01.92,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,You can read "coed bath" from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.92,0:11:03.57,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.57,0:11:05.59,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievable deduction.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.59,0:11:09.95,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,And, at this inn, there happens to be a coed bath, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.87,0:11:15.74,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,The criminal has to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.74,0:11:18.79,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I really don't think that's possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.78,0:11:22.73,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.73,0:11:25.24,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Who could the criminal be?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.24,0:11:26.93,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Continue to the second part.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.23,0:11:31.90,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Kaneme no mono wo! Hayaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.23,0:11:31.90,Note,Note,0000,0000,0000,,Kaneme no mono wo! Hayaku! = Grab the valuables! Fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.13,0:11:36.87,Default,3,0000,0000,0000,,Kuminzei, haratta?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.13,0:11:36.87,Note,Note,0000,0000,0000,,Kuminzei, haratta? = Did you pay your taxes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.16,0:11:41.11,Default,3,0000,0000,0000,,Drop Out Trio's Glutton Dreamy Mood!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.19,0:11:44.03,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.03,0:11:44.94,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.94,0:11:48.46,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,How about we make things clear. Are we to eat or provide a service shot in the hot spring?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.46,0:11:49.36,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.36,0:11:51.12,Default,Ris,0000,0000,0000,,The potency of this spring is-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.00,0:11:54.84,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,Risa-chin, you're supposed to do that after we eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.84,0:11:57.02,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,It's a merry-go-round of flavor!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.02,0:11:59.50,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,No, you haven't eaten one yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.50,0:12:00.50,Default,Ris,0000,0000,0000,,Gilgamesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.50,0:12:01.66,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,That's the wrong show!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.66,0:12:03.00,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,This tastes so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.10,0:12:08.74,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.20,0:12:14.47,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that it looks different from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.77,0:12:19.51,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,M-Maria-san. When did you get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.51,0:12:21.95,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,And, you are the criminal, Maria-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.95,0:12:23.20,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.20,0:12:24.06,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Then why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.62,0:12:27.29,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.29,0:12:30.60,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Sexy shots have to happen in a suspense story.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.15,0:12:38.57,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,We are using a towel for the sake of broadcasting restrictions,\Nbut in reality, please do not use a bath towel in the bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.57,0:12:39.67,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.23,0:12:43.68,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Let's keep this going and let the second "must have" happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.41,0:12:45.71,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Gourmet food scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.95,0:12:47.51,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.51,0:12:50.92,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,Please enjoy the fresh seafood!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.47,0:12:54.55,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,Afterwards, we have a magic show scheduled.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.97,0:12:57.09,Default,Ris,0000,0000,0000,,Here's your lukewarm gasoline.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.62,0:13:00.79,Default,Rob,0000,0000,0000,,Good stuff~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.32,0:13:03.16,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,On to the third "must have"!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.66,0:13:05.86,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Inquiry at a bar!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.93,0:13:10.70,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,So, what do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.25,0:13:14.07,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Does this person ring a bell?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.07,0:13:15.76,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,Ring a bell?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.76,0:13:17.31,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,A loud one!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.90,0:13:25.28,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,That girl is my older sister's friend's cousin\Nand the burglar that took my boyfriend away!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.23,0:13:29.95,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than a suspense show,\Nit's becoming an afternoon soap opera.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.36,0:13:31.46,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Here's the fourth "must have".
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.96,0:13:34.36,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,Mada mada dane!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.48,0:13:38.86,Default-alt,2,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.87,0:13:39.33,Default,Robo,0000,0000,0000,,Advantage, Makimura-Izumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.33,0:13:41.75,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's getting exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.75,0:13:43.67,Default,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,It's all messed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.56,0:13:45.56,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,We have trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.30,0:13:50.09,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Maria-san! You were in the hot spring until now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.09,0:13:50.95,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.95,0:13:55.48,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,I went back to our room once, and I found this terrifying thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.35,0:13:59.23,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Maria? Stop beating around the bush and tell us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.23,0:14:01.10,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,The corpse is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.51,0:14:04.62,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,She's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.62,0:14:05.79,Default,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,It is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.00,0:14:09.09,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,A disappearing body. The most suspenseful moment in a suspense story.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.09,0:14:12.25,Default,Ris,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no. The case is about to become forever wrapped in mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.25,0:14:14.66,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,But, who hid it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.66,0:14:16.73,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,The criminal, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.73,0:14:17.78,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,The criminal?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.78,0:14:22.40,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, must be trying to cause confusion in me to disrupt the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.40,0:14:23.51,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.22,0:14:28.90,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is this all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.90,0:14:31.85,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure they can find the key clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.08,0:14:35.04,Default,SP,0000,0000,0000,,And here's something under the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.75,0:14:37.06,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.06,0:14:39.16,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like a voice recorder.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.16,0:14:40.32,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Show it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.05,0:14:46.84,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the scream we originally heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.84,0:14:48.44,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.44,0:14:49.68,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.68,0:14:50.60,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,What's the significance behind it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.51,0:15:01.68,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,It's here━━━━━━(ﾟ∀ﾟ)━━━━━━!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.43,0:15:04.67,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,The mystery is solved, my dear Watson.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.67,0:15:06.32,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,"M-My dear Watson"...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.82,0:15:09.81,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Next Nagi's hint.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.81,0:15:10.72,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Video.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.05,0:15:15.56,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,So, have you figured out the criminal and the trick behind it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.62,0:15:21.53,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.53,0:15:23.21,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a snack.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.21,0:15:25.81,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I mean, Trick or Treat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.78,0:15:29.27,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,Trick or Treat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.38,0:15:33.64,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait, give me candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.64,0:15:34.78,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,Trick or Treat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.79,0:15:40.20,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,Halloween isn't celebrated around Japan well at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.20,0:15:42.15,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,This is a different kind of trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.70,0:15:47.76,Default,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,Why are we at a place like this all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.76,0:15:53.87,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped. Climax scenes by a cliff are the greatest "must have" in a suspense show.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.11,0:15:57.51,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is perfect if we have Funa**** Jirou.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.86,0:16:00.07,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to explain the truth behind this case now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.54,0:16:01.64,Default,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.64,0:16:05.64,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,The scene of the crime was not that room.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.98,0:16:11.94,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,If we assume the crime took place in a completely different room at a completely different inn, everything makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.94,0:16:15.89,Default,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean? Explain one piece at a time so it makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.89,0:16:16.62,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.54,0:16:23.80,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,First, the criminal met the victim at a certain inn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.83,0:16:29.20,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Recorded the victim's voice during the incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.20,0:16:32.64,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,After that, took the victim to a room at a separate inn that looks similar,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.64,0:16:37.04,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,in other words, carried her into that room we were in, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.40,0:16:33.29,Default-alt,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Wait, wait, wait, it'll show! It'll show! It'll show!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.29,0:16:35.49,Default-alt,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Be gentler with me! No, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.49,0:16:36.45,Default-alt,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Gentler!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.69,0:16:44.84,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,...made others hear the scream using a timer to think that the crime had just happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.84,0:16:44.14,Default-alt,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,You just heard a scream from the inn, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.14,0:16:44.83,Default-alt,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.16,0:16:49.29,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Everything was planned to create an alibi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.49,0:16:53.17,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,Here! Here, here! I have a question!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.17,0:16:54.14,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.14,0:16:55.20,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the proof?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.89,0:16:59.50,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,I think the voice recorder alone is pushing it a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.93,0:17:04.10,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,The greatest proof is on the video we watched.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.76,0:17:06.70,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,In here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.70,0:17:07.57,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Play.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.62,0:17:10.80,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if it's recording fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.80,0:17:11.18,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.67,0:17:15.44,Default,Mak,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see anything suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.44,0:17:18.77,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you notice something about that wall scroll?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.04,0:17:26.71,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,It's completely different from the one in that room.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.71,0:17:27.94,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.94,0:17:31.96,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,The criminal wasn't able to keep an eye open for the wall scroll.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.20,0:17:34.67,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,There are four other mistakes, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.67,0:17:37.23,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Those who get them correct will get-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.28,0:17:41.51,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Coming this far, you all know who the criminal is, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.56,0:17:46.61,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,I remember one person coming late!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.76,0:17:50.18,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,And that individual brought the video, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.63,0:17:55.35,Default,Ris,0000,0000,0000,,She said something about\Na motorbike delivering it and what not.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.35,0:17:59.42,Default,Mak,0000,0000,0000,,But if she is the criminal, then everything does make sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.55,0:18:01.50,Default,Rob,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.57,0:18:04.30,Default,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,M-Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.87,0:18:08.21,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Hinagiku-san, we never thought you'd be the criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.21,0:18:10.42,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,But it was so convincing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.42,0:18:13.03,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. She's the least suspicious of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.03,0:18:14.31,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore she becomes suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.31,0:18:15.44,Default,3,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.08,0:18:21.84,Default,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,That was a wonderful deduction.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.84,0:18:24.33,Default,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought you'd figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.33,0:18:25.45,Default,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, she's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.45,0:18:27.84,Default,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,I am the criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.84,0:18:29.01,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.35,0:18:32.08,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,The criminal is not Hinagiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.08,0:18:34.82,Default,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't take my scene away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.82,0:18:37.21,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,You surprised me so much, the anesthesia burned out in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.17,0:18:41.15,Default,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,From the developments, only I can be the criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.15,0:18:44.05,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,But that would make this all too simple and boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.05,0:18:48.58,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Um, that's making it hard\Nto figure out who's speaking, so can you stop it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.90,0:18:52.49,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,You've all forgotten something!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.49,0:18:56.21,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,There is one more very suspicious person!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.50,0:18:57.62,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,One more person?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.62,0:18:59.48,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! And that individual is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.94,0:19:01.09,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,That individual is?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.55,0:19:07.56,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,The person doing the voice in the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.75,0:19:09.22,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.22,0:19:12.89,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Milady, isn't that getting too absurd?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.89,0:19:14.10,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,No, this is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.32,0:19:18.14,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't think the viewers will accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.14,0:19:21.65,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,It's a suspense story produced and enacted by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.65,0:19:24.11,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let anyone complain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.11,0:19:25.14,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.08,0:19:28.44,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,A tidal wave!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.86,0:19:30.02,Default,Rob,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.02,0:19:31.55,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.78,0:19:33.15,Default,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.15,0:19:37.79,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take this! Why do I not get\Nto come out halfway into the show?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.79,0:19:40.51,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,You're a corpse, so stop coming back to life!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.51,0:19:43.16,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,I can't possibly play dead forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.42,0:19:46.95,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,You screwed up my script I wrote without sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.95,0:19:49.13,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,You leave me without a choice but to use my last resort!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.28,0:19:55.31,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Here comes the service time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.08,0:20:18.43,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,The best thing to do in autumn is to enjoy the hot spring while enjoying the foliage.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.10,0:20:22.58,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,Really, it's so soothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.58,0:20:26.34,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,All of you, too, hope you have a good ****** dreamy mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.57,0:20:30.23,Default,Rob,0000,0000,0000,,This is heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.23,0:20:33.47,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why is the men's bath so small?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.47,0:20:35.47,Default,Rob,0000,0000,0000,,Did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.47,0:20:38.43,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move! It got pinched in!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.43,0:20:40.49,Default,Rob,0000,0000,0000,,What's pinched?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.49,0:20:42.52,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.52,0:20:45.04,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,And so, Glutton Dreamy Mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.04,0:20:47.23,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,It was a twenty-minute long special.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.23,0:20:49.49,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, we'll fight against siblings.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.11,0:20:52.94,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Right, I forgot about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.33,0:20:58.80,Default,Kuz,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have much time left.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.35,0:21:02.17,Default,Kuz,0000,0000,0000,,Come, Mysterious Dark Butler Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.80,0:21:09.48,Default,Kuz,0000,0000,0000,,Defeat the butler Ayasaki Hayate and bring him to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.94,0:21:11.49,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Bring him to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.49,0:21:12.47,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.25,0:21:18.57,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,B-Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.61,0:21:23.53,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.78,0:21:26.76,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.27,0:21:29.10,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,B-Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.56,0:21:33.30,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Hayate Blaster!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.32,0:21:43.35,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,You better remember this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.03,0:21:47.82,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Come whenever you like, Mysterious Butlers!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.82,0:21:50.46,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. What the heck am I doing...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.34,0:23:31.02,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi and...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.23,0:23:32.19,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate's...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.19,0:23:33.96,Default,2,0000,0000,0000,,Butler Network!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.96,0:23:37.37,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Whee! Bounce! Bounce! This is Sanzenin Nagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.37,0:23:38.61,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,This is Ayasaki Hayate.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.61,0:23:40.50,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,I'm your idol, Katsura Yukiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.66,0:23:42.53,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Katsura-sensei, what are you here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.71,0:23:44.41,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you kind, Ayasaki-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.41,0:23:47.61,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,But forget that! When the heck\Nis my character song going to be finished?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.61,0:23:50.71,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,We can't expect many sales from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.71,0:23:53.14,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It might be best to duo with Tama.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.33,0:23:56.25,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Ayasaki-kun, you can talk big now, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.45,0:23:58.02,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Next week's guest will be the Hamster!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.02,0:23:59.27,Default,2,0000,0000,0000,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.38,0:24:05.62,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,So you used to call Sakuya-san\N"Saku-neechan" when you were little, Milady?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.62,0:24:06.79,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,It's a horrid past.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.79,0:24:11.05,Default,Sak,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi never took care of little kids,\Nso she's a brat no matter how much she grows.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.05,0:24:11.99,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make fun of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.99,0:24:16.50,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,If I had younger siblings, then I could take care of them better than Saku.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.50,0:24:18.44,Default,Sak,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure? Then prove it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.44,0:24:19.30,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,You got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.30,0:24:20.67,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Hayate no Gotoku.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.92,0:24:23.62,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Do You Like Rich, Pretty Ladies?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.62,0:24:27.93,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know? Of the Wright brothers,\NOrville, the younger brother, is the first one that flew.
